title: Mahler - Symphony No. 7 - Inbal Frankfurt RSO
description:
Mahler: Symphony No. 7.

Gustav Mahler's Seventh Symphony, recorded by Eliahu Inbal and the Frankfurt Radio Symphony Orchestra and released by Denon in 1987. Even if you already have a favourite performance of this symphony (Bernstein, Solti), you have to hear this one. It is a masterful interpretation given stunning recorded sound.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
